            message: "התוכן עדיין קצר מדי כדי להיחשב כטיוטת מאמר רצינית",
            target: "#postContent",
            prompt: `Expand this MDX/Markdown article body to at least 120 characters of substantive Hebrew prose. Keep MDX components if present. Preserve voice.\nCurrent body:\n${content.slice(0, 800)}${content.length > 800 ? "\n..." : ""}\nReturn ONLY the full improved body (Markdown/MDX).`,
